  m_text: "The classroom buzzes with chatter \u2014 new faces, new beginnings. Alex
    quietly takes a seat, scanning the unfamiliar crowd. A classmate smiles, asks
    where Alex came from, and soon laughter fills the gaps of first-day awkwardness.
    Notes are shared, stories exchanged \u2014 and just like that, loneliness gives
    way to friendship"
